Ma précieuse épée !

80
00:03:08,870 --> 00:03:09,380
Rapide!

81
00:03:09,380 --> 00:03:10,230
Patron, prenez-le.

82
00:03:11,370 --> 00:03:12,470
Chef.

83
00:03:13,590 --> 00:03:15,140
Laissez-moi vous prêter cette épée.

84
00:03:18,390 --> 00:03:19,220
Trois.

85
00:03:19,460 --> 00:03:21,990
J'en ai autant qu'il vous faut.

86
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:26,040
Quatre.

87
00:03:27,740 --> 00:03:30,300
Attaque!

88
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:33,400
Descend-le!

89
00:03:36,380 --> 00:03:37,240
Cinq.

90
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:44,710
Six.

91
00:03:50,180 --> 00:03:50,920
Huit.

92
00:03:55,610 --> 00:03:56,410
Neuf.

93
00:04:04,050 --> 00:04:05,640
Pourquoi est-il huit heures moins six ?

94
